{"tid":2378391,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店盆菜有冇好介紹？？？","createTime":"2021-01-24T12:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T09:14:41.000Z","uid":313203,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"c2ff3a789d4aad0804433c78988bceb9fd9b7add","tid":2378391,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"講返背景先，屋企人港豬，過咗成年都係咁，小弟已經放棄咗導返佢哋向黄，不過係咩黄藍店上，佢哋又冇乜所謂嘅。<br />\n<br />\n而家母今日心血來潮想叫盆菜食(因為睇到太興嘅盆菜廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下咁多位連登食家有冇好介紹，最重要係夠黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其次先係味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100d892819410fbcaec221d8cfad9cc6c1b068e8","tid":2378391,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a0213f78e9ad5ab3b60ee194dcd0fe0cb1cb0de","tid":2378391,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58ee338cca4756a77fe1cdaf3a6a83d416ce7c61","tid":2378391,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:15:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e94350307531c8dd1350cdb94982a57ebecdb1c5","tid":2378391,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:15:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eff71fa7373fa9f617084e9a5c0343bfa91ab23b","tid":2378391,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dff17e509d87c059c675216735e7ef23fe6ce20","tid":2378391,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"有冇好介紹啊"},{"pid":"9a03f5b0c1ac9bcb61d470d140422579e579